name:                log-stats
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            A simple program for viewing numerical data from a repeating format log file.
description:         It outputs one repetition of the input data, using, in place of each number,
                     the average, minimum, maximum, or median from the input data, based on
                     command line flags.
license:             GPL-3
license-file:        LICENSE
author:              Mark Barbone
maintainer:          mark.l.barbone@gmail.com
